<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_785e395a-703b-4da2-b1f9-27284ff5af75" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="NSW"><sptc>J1P1</sptc><title id="_75a091e2-9d64-43bf-a739-2cc859aa25df">Operational energy use and greenhouse gas emissions</title><archive-num> 2019: JP1</archive-num><subclause id="_8cc873f8-78cd-47e7-b5b5-99f6cb07d103" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_6f8a9de8-b102-494a-ba7b-33773125307d">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A building including its <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1456_25.0.0.xml#_242ba975-4cdf-4b84-9f41-b8d524ee17c2" id="_3c5df5c8-79c9-4a8b-bdda-61f754adb3da" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">services</xref>, must have features that—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_708b494d-7372-48a9-b997-8c4f720b8f38">facilitate the efficient use of energy and near zero operational greenhouse gas emissions appropriate to—<ol><li>the function and use of the building; and</li><li>the level of human comfort required for the building use; and</li></ol></li><li id="_16398544-ad87-4803-90c3-15c1892a0484">for the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1225_1.8.0.xml#_26276791-20ad-4404-951f-29b5bff0ff80" id="_c10d4d75-9ab3-40f4-900b-fa8539d1ff97" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">conditioned space</xref>, achieve an hourly <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1429_4.0.0.xml#_044c235a-5f51-4bc7-9eb9-7cfba1a0f023" id="_183729de-272e-4aef-a327-dfcdc5b0f9c8" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">regulated energy</xref> consumption and associated greenhouse gas emissions, averaged over the annual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1341_0.5.0.xml#_22178a20-4ed7-4cee-8507-b36346202638" id="_97d7d1fd-2ef7-42f7-8bdc-cd9ba861ffdd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">hours of operation</xref>, of not more than—<ol><li>for a Class 6 building, 40 kJ/m².hr; and 4 g of CO<sub id="_a5e92b45-e1d2-41d4-90ad-03a78443dcfa">2</sub>-e/m<sup id="_21987a45-8ca7-4b33-bf23-8b09e0015926">2</sup>.hr; and</li><li>for a Class 5, 7b, 8 or 9a building other than a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1512_27.0.0.xml#_d1b612a5-df98-4406-ba1e-237f837e1061" id="_d076ccf0-002b-4099-a871-6e308a275251" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">ward area</xref>, or a Class 9b <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/d5440ff9-b49a-4154-8539-afc815034863/1447_0.6.0.xml#_23515733-4511-421a-8c89-650d33e5f6e4" id="_aad16d56-327f-44d9-991a-b252446947d9" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">school</xref>, 22 kJ/m².hr, and 2.2 g of CO<sub id="_0e94c77c-2e76-45f2-aec9-a90ff7e9d4e7">2</sub>-e/m<sup id="_04025ca0-e3a4-4588-9341-dcffde65c25a">2</sup>.hr; and</li><li>for all other building classifications, 8 kJ/m².hr and 1 g of CO<sub id="_ef831d37-a90a-4275-a6ae-3bdcde6e3928">2</sub>-e/m<sup id="_3c00d809-d77d-41bb-b328-9ffe0a83b945">2</sup>.hr.</li></ol></li></ol></subclause></clause>